 <% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>
<body>

    <h1>Feedback and Complaint Submission</h1>
    <p>Please fill out the form below to provide your feedback or submit a complaint. We value your input and will respond as soon as possible.</p>
    
    <form method="POST" action="/listings">
        <div>
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Insert your name" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Insert your Email" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="contact">Contact:</label>
            <input type="tel" id="contact" name="contact" placeholder="Insert your contact number" required>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="category">Category:</label>
            <select name="category" id="category" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select Category</option>
                <option value="Maintenance">Maintenance</option>
                <option value="Food">Food</option>
                <option value="Security">Security</option>
            </select>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div>
            <label for="description">Description:</label>
            <textarea id="description" name="description" placeholder="Insert description" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <br>
        <form method="GET" action="/" >
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </form>
    
    <h3>Why Your Feedback Matters</h3>
    <p>Your feedback helps us improve our services and address any issues you may have experienced. Whether it's a complaint or a suggestion, we appreciate your input and will work to address it as quickly as possible.</p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">thealgorithmalphas@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    <p>We are continually striving to enhance our services based on your valuable insights. Our commitment to excellence means that every piece of feedback is meticulously reviewed and taken into consideration for future improvements. When you share your feedback, you contribute to a larger community effort to improve and innovate. Each suggestion helps us better understand your needs and tailor our services to meet them more effectively. We pride ourselves on our responsiveness and dedication to customer satisfaction. Whether it's a suggestion for a new feature or a concern that needs addressing, we are here to listen and take action. Your voice truly matters to us. We encourage you to provide as much detail as possible in your feedback. The more information we have, the better equipped we are to address your concerns and implement meaningful changes. Our team includes experts from various fields who are ready to tackle any issues and enhance your experience. Your input is not just a number; it becomes a catalyst for real change and improvement. We are grateful for your engagement and look forward to your continued support. Together, we can make our services better, more efficient, and more enjoyable for everyone. Remember, you can always track the progress of your feedback through our support portal. Transparency and open communication are at the heart of our relationship with our users. Thank you for being a part of our journey and helping us achieve our goals. Your trust and feedback are the foundation of our success, and we are committed to honoring that trust with continuous improvement.</p>
    
</body>
